{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"B\n    \n      Multi-Step Agent Wizard\n      A tabbed/stepped creation flow walking through Identity, Capabilities, Orchestration, and Deployment config. Each step maps to one of your framework stages. The agent form becomes a mini-wizard instead of a single dialog.\n      \n        What you get from your framework:\n        Stage 1: Identity tab (name, persona, security level)\n        Stage 3: Capabilities tab (tool catalog, scoping, HITL toggles)\n        Stage 4: Orchestration tab (architecture choice, fallback logic)\n        Stage 5: Basic deployment config (environment selector)\n        \n        Schema change: ~8 new fields + JSON config column\n        Effort: ~1 day. Needs new UI component.\n        Tradeoff: More complex form, fields won't have real backend logic yet (tool catalog is metadata only, no actual MCP integration)","choice":"b","id":null,"timestamp":1774528222740}
